OL,5,Cscandal?
OL,7,FITV News outlines who exactly was
OL,8,Fresponsible for the disaster, and
OL,9,Fwhether or not they will face
OL,10,Fconsequences.
OL,12,FNHS and doctors
OL,14,FThe risks of blood and blood products
OL,15,Fcausing severe infection were "known
OL,16,Fwell before most patients were
OL,17,Ftreated," the report found.
