OL,7,FYet, patients were not informed of the
OL,8,Frisks or the alternatives, with a
OL,9,Fculture of "doctor knows best"
OL,10,Fprevailing among the ranks of the NHS.
OL,12,FIn some cases, patients were not even
OL,13,Ftold they had been infected, whilst
OL,14,Fothers were informed, but in ways that
OL,15,Fwere "insensitive and inappropriate,"
OL,16,Fthe report found.
