OL,7,FHaematologists of the era have been
OL,8,Falso heavily criticised, including
OL,9,Fleading haematologist, Professor
OL,10,FArthur Bloom, whose opinions
OL,11,F"disastrously" influenced the UK
OL,12,FDepartment for Health and Social
OL,13,FSecurity (DHSS), the report said.
OL,15,FAccording to the report, Prof Bloom
OL,16,Ffailed to pass on warnings and advised
OL,17,Fto continue importing commercial
OL,18,Ffactor concentrates.
