OL,7,FAccording to the inquiry, the
OL,8,Fclinicians were "well aware" of the
OL,9,Frisks of infecting the children, which
OL,10,Fit says were regarded as "objects of
OL,11,Fresearch".
OL,13,FA statement released by the college on
OL,14,FMonday said the inquiry "lays bare the
OL,15,Fsystemic failure at the heart of the
OL,16,Fscandal".
