OL,7,FThe statement continued: "Whilst today
OL,8,Fis about understanding how and why
OL,9,Fpeople were given infected blood
OL,10,Fproducts in the 1970s and 80s, it is
OL,11,Fabsolutely right that the government
OL,12,Fhas committed to establishing a proper
OL,13,Fcompensation scheme.
OL,15,F"We'll now be taking the time to
OL,16,Freflect on the report's wider
OL,17,Frecommendations."
