OL,3,CFrom ministers to NHS doctors: Who is
OL,4,Cto blame for the infected blood
OL,5,Cscandal?
OL,7,FMs Thatcher never apologised for the
OL,8,Fscandal before her death in 2013
OL,9,Fdespite mounting evidence.
OL,11,FWhen asked by victim groups for
OL,12,Fcompensation in 1990, Ms Thatcher
OL,13,Fresponded in a letter: "The government
OL,14,Fhas not accepted that the infection of
OL,15,Fhaemophiliacs with the Aids virus,
OL,16,Ftragic as it is, was the subject of
OL,17,Fnegligence."
